						<div class="postbody">What I do for famitone2 banked songs:<br /><br />1. At the start of FamiToneMusicPlay, &quot;sta _song&quot; to record what song is being played.<br />2. In the music.s file, put the song data to whatever banks, but keep the headers in the common bank. song0ch0 onwards banked IOW. Keep an array of which song is in which bank.<br />3. In NMI, set the new bank right before FamiToneUpdate and restore it after.<br /><br />I haven't needed to bank sounds.</div>

