						<div class="postbody">Normally, this is the sort of technical issue that I love to solve, but I'm on holiday for the next few days.<br /><br />He's a solution. Put a breakpoint on reads on the sfx data.  It will break everywhere that needs the data. Wrap bank switches around those.</div>

					
